headline: Real Estate Is the S&P 500's Best Performer Today
summary: Among all 11 sectors of the S&P 500, real estate is easily the best performer for the day. The S&P 500 Real Estate sector is up 1.4%. It includes real estate investment trust, or REIT, stocks like Ventas and Healthpeak Properties.
